SENATE RESOLUTION No. ___
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED RESOLUTION
A SENATE RESOLUTION expressing the Indiana State
Senate's sincere appreciation to the Indiana State Medical
Association and the Indiana Academy of Family Physicians for
coordinating and operating the "Doctor of the Day" program
and to the dedicated doctors who participated.
